{"service_name": "iClarity CRM and Case Management Solutions Consultancy and Support", "service_id": "5994817557364736", "company_name": "Horizon Software Solutions", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Horizon Software Solutions\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     iClarity CRM and Case Management Solutions Consultancy and Support\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Consultancy and support services for iClarity CRM and Case Management Solutions Framework to identify and address business needs alongside solution development and consultancy services \u2013 system and infrastructure reviews, ICT/Cloud strategy and planning, stakeholder engagement, business cases, requirements capture, system/service design &amp; development, project management, supplier engagement and team support.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Review the potential for iClarity for the organisation/service\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identify which iClarity solutions are best suited to  Client\u2019s needs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Modular approach consultancy, requirement capture, feasibility and implementation support\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Review and assessment of problems and business needs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identify and secure business improvements and integrated services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Maximise new technology and cloud-based solutions and delivery\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Review and identify the need and develop business cases\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Plan the optimum use of technology and access channels\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identification and development of solutions and integration with other systems\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support  iClarity  implementation and integration with other systems\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Modular approach for  iClarity consultancy and implemenation support\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Optimisation of  iClarity to meet business needs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduce and manage operating costs and improve efficiency\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enable better business decisions based on  real-time information\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Avoid duplication and make best use of available data\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Prioiritisation of  activities and implementation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supports improved engagement with customers\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     One view of the customer, sharing information and records\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Benefits realisation strategy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Translating  business requirements into  iClarity solutions\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3450.0 to \u00a3850.0 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Education pricing available\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/93195/5994817557364736-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n 